Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.04,0:40:11.86,English,,0,0,0,,How can you mend your soul and\N{\rChinese}你怎么能修复灵魂？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.86,0:40:16.14,English,,0,0,0,,repair your worldview so that you can live for your family, okay?\N{\rChinese}修整你的世界观，让你能为家人而活，好吗？
